    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Branch of political science dealing primarily with the planning, operation, and supervision of government agencies, programs, and functions, as well as the determination and implementation of public policy.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
